Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.51,0:22:18.24,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}おはよう世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.24,0:22:21.31,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fsp0\rop-cn\blur2}Good Morning World!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.47,0:22:34.98,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}何れ程　歩いたろう？
